WEBVTT

00:01.305 --> 00:02.393
[Boyd] Previously, on From...

00:02.524 --> 00:03.612
There's darkness in the forest,

00:03.742 --> 00:07.094
nightmares you can't even
begin to imagine.

00:07.224 --> 00:08.443
[children]
Anghkooey. Anghkooey.

00:08.573 --> 00:10.793
No, no, no, no,
no, no, no!

00:10.923 --> 00:12.664
Don't touch me. Don't touch me!
Don't, don't!

00:12.795 --> 00:14.318
Anghkooey.

00:14.449 --> 00:16.799
-[shouts]
-Hey, hey! You okay?

00:16.929 --> 00:19.323
-Did you see them?
-See what? See who?

00:19.454 --> 00:22.718
[Victor] Eloise said that's
where my mother went that night,

00:22.848 --> 00:25.329
the night
the bad things happened.

00:25.460 --> 00:28.202
She went to save the children
locked in the tower.

00:28.332 --> 00:29.681
[Kenny]
This mean a lot to you?

00:29.812 --> 00:31.205
-Don't. Please.
-Yeah? Fuck you!

00:32.467 --> 00:34.034
You ever come near
my mom again,

00:34.164 --> 00:35.513
I will drag
your fucking psycho ass

00:35.644 --> 00:36.819
into that Box myself.

00:36.949 --> 00:39.300
We, uh, pulled something
out of that thing.

00:39.430 --> 00:41.345
Only problem is we gotta
figure out how to get this

00:41.476 --> 00:42.694
inside another one
of those things

00:42.825 --> 00:44.218
without getting ourselves
killed.

00:44.348 --> 00:46.220
So make some silver bullets.

00:47.351 --> 00:50.441
Well, you think this place is
one big experiment, right?

00:50.572 --> 00:52.574
And it never occurred to you

00:52.704 --> 00:54.706
that some of the people here
might be in on it?

00:54.837 --> 00:56.404
I mean, they'd have to be.

00:56.534 --> 00:58.667
How else do you keep
the experiment on track?

01:01.452 --> 01:03.150
Randall, what the fuck?

01:03.280 --> 01:05.412
New plan.

01:05.543 --> 01:07.806
[Kristi] Elgin had a dream
that he was drowning

01:07.937 --> 01:09.373
and he started
spitting up water,

01:09.504 --> 01:12.202
and you had cicadas
in your dreams, and...

01:12.333 --> 01:14.291
When the music box
started playing,

01:14.422 --> 01:17.077
one of them jumped out
and it burned my arm.

01:17.207 --> 01:18.643
Are you honestly saying
that our fucking dreams

01:18.774 --> 01:20.384
can hurt us now?

01:20.515 --> 01:22.343
-[buzzing]
-Do you hear that?

01:22.473 --> 01:24.126
[Reggie] Help me!

01:24.257 --> 01:26.781
Please.
Please. I need help!

01:39.708 --> 01:40.796
She said, um...

01:42.711 --> 01:44.800
She said she was gonna
take a nap.

01:47.194 --> 01:48.760
I was downstairs.

01:50.719 --> 01:52.416
And I heard her
screaming.

01:54.418 --> 01:56.551
I-I came in and I--

01:56.681 --> 01:59.206
I started
shaking her, and...

01:59.336 --> 02:00.598
[sobs briefly]

02:01.425 --> 02:04.298
...trying to wake her up,
and, um, she kept...

02:05.908 --> 02:08.606
She was talking
in her sleep,

02:08.737 --> 02:12.610
saying something
over and over.

02:14.525 --> 02:16.353
And then she, uh...

02:16.484 --> 02:20.749
Something cracked inside her,

02:20.879 --> 02:24.318
and her body
and her face...

02:25.928 --> 02:28.757
Oh, God. Jesus.

02:29.932 --> 02:31.368
What did she say?

02:31.499 --> 02:33.327
[Reggie]
What?

02:33.457 --> 02:36.285
You said she was talking.
What did she say?

02:36.417 --> 02:38.549
I don't--

02:38.680 --> 02:39.594
Hey, hey, Reggie.

02:39.724 --> 02:40.898
I can't. No.

02:41.030 --> 02:43.902
Reggie, Reggie. Hey.
Listen, Reggie.

02:44.033 --> 02:46.208
I need you...

02:46.340 --> 02:49.212
I need you to tell me
what she said.

02:54.739 --> 02:56.567
It was, um...

02:59.744 --> 03:02.704
"They touch.
They break..."

03:06.925 --> 03:08.318
"They steal..."

03:09.624 --> 03:11.539
No one here
is free."

03:14.585 --> 03:15.847
And then she just...

03:17.545 --> 03:18.981
Her face just fucking...

03:20.025 --> 03:22.637
[cries]

03:22.767 --> 03:24.682
And was she still
asleep?

03:24.813 --> 03:25.944
Are you sure
she was asleep?

03:26.075 --> 03:28.164
Yes, I'm fucking sure!

03:28.295 --> 03:30.166
Okay, okay.

03:30.297 --> 03:32.647
All right.
Okay.

03:32.777 --> 03:34.953
[sobs]

03:35.083 --> 03:36.477
We need to, um...

03:37.956 --> 03:41.177
Yeah. Um, okay.

03:41.308 --> 03:43.309
Okay. Okay.

03:44.789 --> 03:49.446
[sobs]

03:49.577 --> 03:51.840
No.

03:51.970 --> 03:54.582
[cicadas buzz]

04:10.684 --> 04:12.382
Is everything
all right?

04:12.513 --> 04:14.819
Oh, yeah, little man.
Everything's great.

04:14.949 --> 04:16.821
Hey, do me a favor.

04:16.952 --> 04:19.520
Do you mind heading home
for me, okay?

04:19.650 --> 04:23.567
And do you mind if your sister
stays here for a bit?

04:25.787 --> 04:26.744
Thanks, bud.

04:26.875 --> 04:28.006
[Julie]
Yeah.

04:28.137 --> 04:29.878
Go on home.
I'll be right behind you.

04:30.008 --> 04:31.532
[Ethan] Okay.

04:33.708 --> 04:35.013
[Tian-Chen
speaks Cantonese]

04:35.144 --> 04:36.406
We go.

04:36.537 --> 04:37.842
You come help
make dinner.

04:37.973 --> 04:39.714
[Ethan]
All right.

04:39.844 --> 04:42.324
[cicadas continue buzzing]

04:42.456 --> 04:43.544
Kenny.

04:44.849 --> 04:47.069
Listen, we gotta--

04:47.199 --> 04:49.680
We gotta tell
the people door to door.

04:49.811 --> 04:51.856
Okay? We got 30 minutes left
of daylight.

04:51.987 --> 04:55.382
You and Julie cover the town.
I'll go to Colony House.

04:55.512 --> 04:57.471
Reggie will come with me.

04:57.601 --> 04:59.734
We can't leave anyone alone.

04:59.864 --> 05:01.562
What about Sara?

05:03.041 --> 05:05.827
Boyd, what's going on?

05:05.957 --> 05:07.002
What happened in there?

05:10.005 --> 05:11.441
Something killed Paula.

05:13.225 --> 05:15.837
But it's not dark yet.
I don't...

05:15.967 --> 05:18.448
There's something else here now.
Something new.

05:22.104 --> 05:23.801
It's not safe for anyone
to go to sleep tonight.

05:23.932 --> 05:25.020
Okay?

05:26.413 --> 05:27.805
My dad.

05:27.936 --> 05:29.111
He's out at the RV.

05:30.155 --> 05:31.461
Okay.

05:31.592 --> 05:34.595
Randall, what the fuck?

05:34.725 --> 05:36.597
[Randall]
It's a new plan.

05:37.901 --> 05:40.078
I'm gonna fucking kill you.

05:40.209 --> 05:41.993
Oh, yeah?

05:42.124 --> 05:43.821
[Jim] What are you--
What are you doing?

05:43.952 --> 05:45.432
Donna,
I'm so sorry.

05:45.562 --> 05:49.000
Don't apologize to her.
We were right.

05:49.131 --> 05:51.002
She's fucking part of this.

05:51.133 --> 05:52.656
Part of what?

05:54.441 --> 05:57.400
I saw you,
up at the clinic.

05:57.531 --> 05:59.968
Yeah, that's right.
I followed you.

06:00.098 --> 06:03.580
They were carrying one of their
monsters out of the clinic.

06:03.711 --> 06:06.801
Well, what are they,
some kind of animatronic?

06:06.931 --> 06:08.672
You got a faulty model, huh?

06:08.803 --> 06:10.065
That was a body,
you dumb shit.

06:10.195 --> 06:11.327
Okay.

06:11.458 --> 06:12.807
Boyd killed
one of them.

06:12.937 --> 06:14.591
He what?

06:14.722 --> 06:16.376
He killed one of
the monsters.

06:16.506 --> 06:18.160
So, now they can fucking die?

06:18.290 --> 06:20.728
It's funny how suddenly
the rules fucking change

06:20.858 --> 06:22.860
once someone catches out
your bullshit.

06:22.991 --> 06:24.471
Are you fucking
kidding me?

06:26.473 --> 06:28.170
I thought you'd be more...

06:29.867 --> 06:31.695
This was your idea.

06:31.826 --> 06:34.002
No. This?

06:34.132 --> 06:35.960
This is fucking crazy.

06:36.091 --> 06:38.093
This was not part
of the plan.

06:38.223 --> 06:40.138
She's part of the reason
we're still here!

06:40.269 --> 06:41.488
Fuck her!

06:41.618 --> 06:42.967
We are not doing this.

06:46.841 --> 06:50.148
You know what
I'm starting to think, Jim?

06:50.279 --> 06:52.368
That maybe you just put
this shit in my head

06:52.499 --> 06:54.414
to see what I would do.

06:54.544 --> 06:56.938
How do I know that
you're not part of this, huh?

06:57.068 --> 06:59.897
'Cause my house collapsed
on top of me.

07:00.028 --> 07:01.856
What the fuck
is wrong with you?

07:03.161 --> 07:04.554
Here. This one.

07:04.685 --> 07:06.034
-Asshole!
-Oof.

07:06.164 --> 07:08.949
[Jim groans]

07:10.255 --> 07:11.822
Jim?

07:11.953 --> 07:14.042
You wanna dance, Jim?

07:14.172 --> 07:16.436
[gunshot]

07:17.567 --> 07:21.049
Drop the fucking knife.

07:22.180 --> 07:23.225
You gonna shoot me?

07:28.317 --> 07:29.449
Okay.

07:30.798 --> 07:32.669
Now, stand over there.

07:38.632 --> 07:39.633
You all right, Jim?

07:39.763 --> 07:41.591
Yeah.
I'm so sorry.

07:41.722 --> 07:42.766
This wasn't
supposed to happen.

07:42.897 --> 07:44.072
Get her.

07:44.202 --> 07:46.727
Just get me off
this fucking tree.

07:48.816 --> 07:50.252
We got about five minutes

07:50.382 --> 07:51.819
to get in that van
and get back to town.

07:51.949 --> 07:53.124
Who's got the key?

07:53.255 --> 07:54.952
-I don't know.
-[Boyd] Jim?

07:55.083 --> 07:56.998
Oh, you mean,
uh, these keys?

07:58.173 --> 07:59.827
-Hey, don't!
-[shouts]

07:59.957 --> 08:01.437
Oh, fuck.

08:01.568 --> 08:03.265
Are you outta
your goddamn mind?

08:03.395 --> 08:05.093
Guess we're gonna have
to stay the night

08:05.223 --> 08:07.225
and see what happens, huh?

08:12.796 --> 08:15.277
